    <entry>
      <title>hexo博客搭建记录</title>
      <link href="/2023/10/29/hexo%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%B0%E5%BD%95/"/>
      <url>/2023/10/29/hexo%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%B0%E5%BD%95/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1><span id="hexo-bo-ke-da-jian-ji-lu">hexo博客搭建记录</span><a href="#hexo-bo-ke-da-jian-ji-lu" class="header-anchor"></a></h1><p>目录跳转：</p><div class="toc"><!-- toc --><ul><li><a href="#da-jian-hexo-bo-ke">搭建hexo博客</a><ul><li><a href="#1-qian-zhi-huan-jing">1.前置环境</a></li><li><a href="#2-an-zhuang-hexo">2.安装hexo</a></li><li><a href="#3-chu-shi-hua-hexo">3.初始化hexo</a></li><li><a href="#4-hexo-sheng-cheng-jing-tai-wang-ye-wen-jian">4.hexo生成静态网页文件</a></li><li><a href="#5-kai-qi-hexo-fu-wu">5.开启hexo服务</a></li><li><a href="#6-bu-shu-bo-ke">6.部署博客</a></li></ul></li></ul><!-- tocstop --></div><p>花了一下午把hexo博客搭好了，这里简单记录一下搭建的过程。</p><h2><span id="da-jian-hexo-bo-ke">搭建hexo博客</span><a href="#da-jian-hexo-bo-ke" class="header-anchor"></a></h2><h3><span id="1-qian-zhi-huan-jing">1.前置环境</span><a href="#1-qian-zhi-huan-jing" class="header-anchor"></a></h3><ul><li><p>Git</p><p>由于博客是搭在git上的，因此需要绑定好 Github 的账号与邮箱，并能够建立连接</p><p>具体操作请参考：<a href="https://t3uk1.github.io/2023/10/29/Git的绑定与连接" target="_blank">Git的绑定与连接</a></p></li><li><p>Node.js</p></li></ul><h3><span id="2-an-zhuang-hexo">2.安装hexo</span><a href="#2-an-zhuang-hexo" class="header-anchor"></a></h3><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm install -g hexo-cli# npm 安装 hexo</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3><span id="3-chu-shi-hua-hexo">3.初始化hexo</span><a href="#3-chu-shi-hua-hexo" class="header-anchor"></a></h3><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo init blog# 初始化 hexo</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>其中，<em><strong>blog</strong></em> 为博客的根目录，其名称可以自定义。</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">cd blog# 切换到博客根目录</span><br><span class="line">npm install# 自动化安装依赖文件，完成 hexo 初始化</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3><span id="4-hexo-sheng-cheng-jing-tai-wang-ye-wen-jian">4.hexo生成静态网页文件</span><a href="#4-hexo-sheng-cheng-jing-tai-wang-ye-wen-jian" class="header-anchor"></a></h3><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo generate# 自动化生成静态网页文件</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>该命令可以简写为</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo g</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3><span id="5-kai-qi-hexo-fu-wu">5.开启hexo服务</span><a href="#5-kai-qi-hexo-fu-wu" class="header-anchor"></a></h3><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo server# 开启服务</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>开启hexo服务后，即可通过本地访问 blog 页面（默认为 <code>localhost:4000</code> ）预览博客页面。</p><p>相关参数：</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo s# 简化指令</span><br><span class="line">hexo s -s# 静态模式</span><br><span class="line">hexo s -p 5000# 更改端口</span><br><span class="line">hexo s -i 192.168.1.5# 自定义ip</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3><span id="6-bu-shu-bo-ke">6.部署博客</span><a href="#6-bu-shu-bo-ke" class="header-anchor"></a></h3><p>这里使用Github仓库进行部署。</p><p>首先在Github创建一个名为  <code>&lt;username&gt;.github.io</code>的仓库，例如我的就是<code>t3uk1.github.io</code>。</p><p>在博客根目录下安装 <code>hexo-deployer-git</code> 部署插件</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm install hexo-deployer-git --save</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>更改 hexo 站点配置文件 (<code>~/_config.yml</code>) 中的 Deployment配置项</p><p>以我为例更改的配置项结果为</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">deploy:</span><br><span class="line">  type: git</span><br><span class="line">  repo: git@github.com:t3uk1/t3uk1.github.io.git</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><blockquote><p>上面<code>repo</code> 使用 ssh 链接的原因：我的 git 使用 ssh 与 github 进行远程连接</p><p>如果git 使用 https 与 github 进行远程连接请使用 https 链接</p></blockquote><p>在<strong>博客根目录</strong>下，输入部署指令</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo deploy# 部署指令</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>简化指令：</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo d</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>一键部署指令：</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo clean &amp;&amp; hexo g -d</span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta prompt_"># </span><span class="language-bash">clean 用于清除本地缓存</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta prompt_"># </span><span class="language-bash">g自动化生成</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta prompt_"># </span><span class="language-bash">-d部署</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>等待一段时间后，可以通过 <code>https://&lt;username&gt;.github.io</code> 访问自己的博客。</p><p>例如我的链接就是：<a href="https://t3uk1.github.io/">https://t3uk1.github.io/</a></p>]]></content>
      
      
      <categories>
          
          <category> hexo </category>
          
      </categories>
      
      
        <tags>
            
            <tag> hexo </tag>
            
        </tags>
      
    </entry>
    
    
    
    <entry>
      <title>Git的绑定与连接</title>
      <link href="/2023/10/29/Git%E7%9A%84%E7%BB%91%E5%AE%9A%E4%B8%8E%E8%BF%9E%E6%8E%A5/"/>
      <url>/2023/10/29/Git%E7%9A%84%E7%BB%91%E5%AE%9A%E4%B8%8E%E8%BF%9E%E6%8E%A5/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1><span id="git-de-bang-ding-yu-lian-jie">Git的绑定与连接</span><a href="#git-de-bang-ding-yu-lian-jie" class="header-anchor"></a></h1><div class="toc"><!-- toc --><ul><li><a href="#pei-zhi-git-de-user">配置Git的User</a></li><li><a href="#shi-yong-ssh-fang-shi-yuan-cheng-lian-jie-git">使用SSH方式远程连接Git</a></li></ul><!-- tocstop --></div><h2><span id="pei-zhi-git-de-user">配置Git的User</span><a href="#pei-zhi-git-de-user" class="header-anchor"></a></h2><p>打开Git Bash（或命令行）</p><p>配置全局name：</p><ul><li><p>github用户名</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">git config --global user.name name</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ul><p>配置全局email：</p><ul><li><p>github邮箱：</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">git config --global user.email email</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ul><p>以我自己的github账户为例：</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">git config --global user.name t3uk1</span><br><span class="line">git config --global user.email xxx@qq.com</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2><span id="shi-yong-ssh-fang-shi-yuan-cheng-lian-jie-git">使用SSH方式远程连接Git</span><a href="#shi-yong-ssh-fang-shi-yuan-cheng-lian-jie-git" class="header-anchor"></a></h2><p>打开Git Bash（或命令行）</p><p>在本地生成对应邮箱的<strong>SSH RSA公钥密钥</strong></p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">ssh-keygen -t rsa</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>使用<strong>默认生成路径</strong>，<strong>默认空key</strong>，这样就可以无需认证直接连接，如果想要设置秘钥也可以设置。</p><p>前往 <code>~/.ssh</code> 目录下寻找密钥（其中默认**<code>id_rsa</code><strong>是密钥信息，</strong><code>id_rsa.pub</code>**为公钥信息）</p><p>在 <strong>Github</strong> 中新建 <strong>SSH keys</strong>：</p><p>github→ Settings→SSH and GPG keys→右上角new SSH key， 打开界面如下：</p><p><img src="image-20231029205623302.png" alt="新增SSH"></p><p>其中<em>Title</em>可以随意填，<em>Key</em>中内容填的是前面生成的(<strong>id_rsa.pub</strong>)的文件内容即公钥信息。</p><p>创建完成后，运行下面的指令，若出现下图情况则说明成功。</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">ssh git@github.com</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><img src="image-20231029205914245.png" alt="success"></p>]]></content>
      
      
      <categories>
          
          <category> Git </category>
          
      </categories>
      
      
        <tags>
            
            <tag> github </tag>
            
            <tag> SSH连接 </tag>
            
        </tags>
      
    </entry>
    
    
    
